# Project Structure Requirements

## Package Managers
- Python projects must use UV exclusively
- JavaScript/TypeScript projects must use PNPM exclusively
- Package manager versions must be locked down
- No other package managers are permitted

## Code Quality Tools
- JavaScript/TypeScript projects must use Biome for:
  - Linting
  - Formatting
  - Type checking
- No ESLint, Prettier or other formatters/linters allowed

## Licensing
- Project must specify a license
- LICENSE file must be included
- License must be documented in package.json
- License compatibility must be validated
